{"word":"ἀπάτη","slug":"ἀπάτη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπάτη</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>prob. from <el>ἅπτομαι</el>, <a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <a href='S:ἀπαφίσκω'><el>ἀπαφίσκω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a trick, fraud, deceit</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>: <i>a stratagem</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>wiles</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>guile, fraud, deceit, treachery</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic<p/></div>"}]}